  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scanning rotations to maximize marker detection.",
    "Immediately switch to marker approach when marker_seen, using move_to_marker.",
    "On marker_close, stop to complete the task safely.",
    "After any obstacle recovery or forward commit, insert a scan state to avoid long straight runs.",
    "Use commit states for all primary actions to prevent oscillations and ensure persistence.",
    "Handle all uncontrollable events in every state to guarantee safe and robust operation.",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front; always pass through a recovery or scan state first.",
    "Prioritize marker approach over exploration when marker is seen.",
    "Return to exploration (scan) only if marker is lost.",
    "Avoid both clockwise and counterclockwise rotation options in the same state to prevent oscillations."
